title: Number of births in Norway 2008 to 2018
summary: In general Number of live births has stayed the same over the Year.
Number of live births is gradually decreasing from 2009 to 2011, roughly constant from 2011 to 2012, slightly decreasing from 2012 to 2013, and finally roughly constant from 2013 to 2016.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2012 and 2013.
The highest Number of live births, of value 61807.0 was reached at Year 2009
Minimum Number of live births about 58890.0 was reached at Year 2016
